===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|hamlet}}, {{m|enm|hamelet}}, a borrowing from {{der|en|fro|hamelet}}, diminutive of {{der|en|fro|hamel}} (Modern {{cog|fr|hameau}}), in turn diminutive of {{der|en|fro|ham}}, of {{der|en|gem}} origin. Cognates include {{cog|en|home}}, {{cog|nl|heem}}, {{cog|de|Heim}}, {{cog|ang|hām}}.

